|E come noi... ciascuno~: In Matt. 6:12, this
verse of the Lord's Prayer reads: "Et dimitte nobis debita
nostra, sicut et nos dimittimus debitoribus nostris."  ("And
forgive us our debts, as we also forgive our debtors.")
